.el .ds Aq '
.TH cdf-state-show 1  "cdf-state-show "
.SH NAME
cdf\-state\-show \- Show the selected durable record
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcdf state show\fR [\fB\-\-pipeline\fR] [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-\-scope\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR]... [\fB\-\-color\fR] [\fB\-\-scope\-json\fR] [\fB\-\-progress\fR] [\fB\-\-unicode\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIRESOURCE\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Show the selected durable record
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-pipeline\fR \fI<ID>\fR
Pipeline identifier
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress progress and non\-primary success narration
.TP
\fB\-\-scope\fR \fI<KEY=VALUE>\fR
Checkpoint scope entry as key=value; may be repeated
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Show evidence detail; repeat for diagnostics
.TP
\fB\-\-color\fR \fI<WHEN>\fR
Color policy: auto, always, or never
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
auto
.IP \(bu 2
always
.IP \(bu 2
never
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-scope\-json\fR \fI<JSON>\fR
Checkpoint scope encoded as JSON
.TP
\fB\-\-progress\fR \fI<WHEN>\fR
Progress policy: auto, always, or never
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
auto
.IP \(bu 2
always
.IP \(bu 2
never
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-unicode\fR \fI<WHEN>\fR
Unicode policy: auto, always, or never
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
auto
.IP \(bu 2
always
.IP \(bu 2
never
.RE
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIRESOURCE\fR]
Resource identifier
